    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) reflects the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol; the team accepted this limitation given the high consistency between two independent laboratories and the conservative nature of the acceptance bounds. Overall credibility is sufficient for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence context of use. Package is filed under ProfileMinimal; signature workflow is pending and will be applied prior to regulatory submission.",
